speaking to you again!

940
01:02:21,400 --> 01:02:22,440
David!

941
01:02:28,680 --> 01:02:30,240
David!

942
01:02:33,360 --> 01:02:34,400
David?

943
01:02:39,600 --> 01:02:40,640
David!

944
01:02:42,720 --> 01:02:44,280
( Screaming )

945
01:02:52,600 --> 01:02:55,720
