954
01:03:22,240 --> 01:03:24,320
I need to see those police reports.

955
01:03:26,400 --> 01:03:27,960
( Sighing )

956
01:03:31,600 --> 01:03:33,680
All right. You got a fax?

957
01:03:33,680 --> 01:03:35,240
Uh-huh, at the school.

958
01:03:35,240 --> 01:03:39,400
Okay. In the morning.
But before breakfast,

959
01:03:39,400 --> 01:03:42,000
because it sure as hell
ain't rated "G."

960
01:03:42,000 --> 01:03:43,040
