997
01:05:51,480 --> 01:05:54,080
God! I wish I was.

998
01:05:57,200 --> 01:06:00,840
Maybe it wasn't an accident.

999
01:06:00,840 --> 01:06:01,880
What?

1000
01:06:01,880 --> 01:06:03,960
Maybe he was being punished.

1001
01:06:03,960 --> 01:06:06,040
