1002
01:06:06,040 --> 01:06:09,160
He killed Rosie.

1003
01:06:09,160 --> 01:06:11,240
Mikey, that's sick.

1004
01:06:11,240 --> 01:06:12,800
I thought you loved her.

1005
01:06:12,800 --> 01:06:13,840
